CityAreaCard - Class in card.city
This is a wrapper around the board areas to hold the state of a city card.
City cards belong to players and can be played once per round (except for AnkhMorporkArea.SMALL_GODS.
CityAreaCard(AnkhMorporkArea) - Constructor for class card.city.CityAreaCard
 
clearAllPieces() - Method in class gameplay.BoardArea
Removes all the pieces from this area (minions, trouble marker, building).
From what I understand these are not handed back to the players.
